hadiths[71]{hadithnumber,text}:
1548,"Musalmanon key eik lashkar ney jis key Ameer Salman Faarsi they, Faras key eik qil'e ka muhaasra (gheraaw) kiya, logon ney kaha : abu-Adbullah ! kya hum un par hamla na kar den?  unhoney kaha : mujhey chhod do main un kafiron ko Islam ki dawat isi tarah dun jaisa ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko unhen dawat detey huye suna hai padhi. , chunanche Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) unkey paas gaey, aur kafiron sey kaha : main tumhari hi qom Faras ka rehney wala eik aadmi hun, tum dekh rahey ho Arab meri itaat kartey hain, agar tum Islam qubul karogey to tumharey liye wohi huquq hongey jo hamarey liye hain, aur tumharey ooper wohi zimme-daariyan aaid hongi jo hamarey ooper hain, aur agar tum apney Deen hi par qaaim rehna chahtey ho to hum usi par tum ko chhod dengey, aur tum zaleel aur khuwar ho kar apney haath sey jiziya ada karo, Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) ney is baat ko Faarsi zaban mein bhi bayan kiya, aur ye bhi kaha : tum qabile-tareef log nahin ho, aur agar tum ney inkar kiya to hum tum sey (haq par) jang karengey, un logon ney jawab diya : hum wo nahin hain ke jiziya den , balke tum sey jang kerengey, musalmanon ney kaha : abu-Adbullah ! kya hum un par hamla na kar den ? unhoney kaha : nahin, phir unhoney teen din tak isi tarah in ko Islam ki dawat di, phir musalmanon sey kaha : un par hamla karo, hum logon ney un par hamla kiya aur us qil'e ko Fateh kar liya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, hum is ko sirf Ata bin Saaib hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail (Imam Bukhari ( ko kehtey huye suna : Abul-Bakhtari ney Salman ko nahin paya hai, isliye ke unhoney Ali ko nahin paya hai, aur Salman ki wafat Ali sey pehley hui hai. 3- is bab mein Barida , Noman bin Muqrin , ibne-Umar aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ki yehi raey hai ke qitaal sey pehley kafiron ko dawat di jaeygi, Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai ke agar in ko pehley Islam ki dawat dey di jaey to behtar hai, ye unkey liye khof ka baais hoga. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke is daur mein dawat ki zarurat nahin hai, Imam Ahmed kehtey hain : main is zamaney mein kisi ko dawat diye janey key laaiq nahin samajhta. 5- Imam Shafai kehtey hain : dawat sey pehley dushmanon sey jang na shuru ki jaey, haan agar kuffar khud jang mein pehal kar bethein to us surat mein agar dawat na di gaee to koi harj nahin kyonkey Islam ki dawat un tak pahunch chuki hai."
1549,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab koi lashkar ya sariya bhejtey to un sey farmatey : ''jab tum koi masjid dekho ya muazzan ki aawaz suno to kisi ko na maaro.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur ye ibn Uena sey aai hai."
1550,"Jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khaibar rawana huye to wahan raat ko pahunchey , aur aap jab bhi kisi qom key paas raat ko pahunchtey to jab tak subah na ho jati is par hamla nahin kartey, phir jab subah ho gaee to Yahud apney phaawdey aur tokriyon key sath nikley , jab unhoney aap ko dekha to kaha : Muhammad hain, Allah ki qism , Muhammad lashkar key sath aa'gey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allahu-Akbar ! khaibar barbad ho gaya, jab hum kisi qom key maidan mein utartey hain us waqt daraaiye gaey logon ki subah , badi buri hoti hai."
1551,Jab Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kisi qom par ghalib aatey to unkey maidan mein teen din tak qiyam kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Humed ki hadees jo Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey aai hai Hasan sahih hai. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney raat mein hamla karney aur chhapa maarney ki ijazat di hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm is ko makrooh samajhtey hain. 5- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke raat mein dushman par chhapa maarney mein koi harj nahin hai. 6- (وافق محمد الخميس) mein (الخميس) sey murad lashkar hai.
1552,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney banu Nazeer key khajuron key darkht jalwa aur katwaa diye padhi. , ye maqame-buwera ka waqia hai, is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil ki :(ما قطعتم من لينة أو تركتموها قائمة على أصولها فبإذن الله وليخزي الفاسقين) ''(musalmano !), (yahud bani Nazir key) khajuron key darkht jo kaat daley hain ya in ko haath bhi na lagaya aur apney tanon par hi in ko khada chhod diya to ye sab Allah key hukm sey tha aur Shan wale Allah ko manzoor tha ke wo nafarmanon ko zaleel karey (Al Hashra :5).""  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi maslak hai, wo darkht kaatney aur qiley wiran karney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm is ko makrooh samajhtey hain, Auzaai ka yehi qol hai. 5- Auzaai kehtey hain : abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney Yazeed ko phal daar darkht kaatney aur makaan wiran karney sey mana kiya, unkey baad musalmanon ney isi par amal kiya. 6- Shafai kehtey hain : dushman key mulk mein aag laganey , darkht aur phal kaatney mein koi harj nahin hai. 7- Ahmed kehtey hain : Islaami lashkar kabhi kabhi aisi jagah hota hai jahan uskey siwa koi chaara nahin hota, lekin bila zarurat aag na lagai jaey. 8- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : aag lagana sunnat hai, jab ye kafiron ki haar aur ruswai ka baais ho."
1553,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney mujhey Anbiya aur Rasulon par Fazilat bakhshi hai.'' ya aap ney ye farmaya : ''meri ummat ko dusri ummaton par fazilat bakhshi hai, aur hamarey liye maale-ghanimat ko halal kiya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Umama ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Abu-Zar , Abdullah bin Amr , abu-Musa aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1554,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maale ghanimat ki taqseem mein ghodey ko do hissey aur aadmi ( sawar ( ko eik hissa diya.
1555,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey behtareen sathi wo hain jinki tadaad chaar ho, aur sab sey behtar sariya wo hai jiski tadaad chaar sau ho, aur sab sey behtar fauj wo hai jiski tadaad chaar hazar ho aur baara hazar Islaami fauj tadaad ki kami ki baais maghloob (parajit) nahin hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Jareer bin Hazim key siwa kisi badey muhaddis sey ye hadees musnadan marvi (riwayat hui) nahin, Zohri ney isey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai. 3- is hadees ko Hibban bin Ali Anzi basanad (Aqeel an Zohri an Ubedullah bin Abdullah an ibne-Abbas an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai, neez (isi ke sath) isey Les bin Saad ney basanad (Aqeel an Zohri an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) mursalan riwayat kiya hai."
1556,"Najda bin Aamir Haroori ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas ye sawal likh kar bheja kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aurton ko sath ley kar jihad kartey they? aur kya aap unkey liye maale ghanimat sey hissey bhi muqarrar farmatey they? ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney in ko jawab mein likha : tum ney merey paas ye sawal likha hai : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aurton ko sath ley kar jihad kartey they? padhi. haan , aap unkey sath jihad kartey they, wo bimaron ka ilaj karti thin aur maale-ghanimat sey in ko (bator inaam) kuchh diya jata tha, reh gaee hissey ki baat to aap ney unkey liye hissea nahin muqarrar kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas aur Umme Atiya Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai ka bhi yehi qol hai, baaz log kehtey hain : aurat aur bachche ko bhi hissa diya jaeyga, Auzaai ka yehi qol hai. 4- Auzaai kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khaibar mein bachchon ko hissey diye aur musalmanon key Ameeron (Haakimon) ney har us bachchey key liye hissey muqarrar kiye jo dushmanon ki sar zamin mein paida huwa ho, Auzaai kehtey hain : Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khaibar mein aurton ko hissey diye aur aap key baad musalmanon ney isi par amal kiya hai."
1557,"Main apney maalikon key sath ghazwae-khaibar mein shareek huwa , unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey merey silsiley mein guftgu ki aur aap ko bataya ke main ghulam hun, chunanche aap ney hukm diya aur merey jism par talwaar latka di gaee, main (chhota qaamat (qad) honey aur talwaar key badi honey key sabab) usey ghaseet'taa tha, aap ney merey liye maale-ghanimat sey kuchh saman deney ka hukm diya, mainey aap key samney wo dam, jhaad phunk pesh kiya jis sey main diwaanon ko jhaad phunk karta tha, aap ney mujhey us ke kuchh hissey chhod deney aur kuchh yad rakhney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke ghulam ko hissa nahin milega albatta Atiya key tor par usey kuchh diya jaeyga, Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai."
1558,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Badr key liye nikley, jab aap Harra al wabra pahunchey to aap key sath eik mushrik ho liya jiski jur'at aur dileri mashhoor thi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey puchha : tum Allah aur uskey Rasool par eman rakhtey ho? usney jawab diya : nahin, aap ney farmaya : ''lot jaao, main kisi mushrik sey hergiz madad nahin lunga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hadees mein is sey bhi ziyada kuchh tafsil hai. 2- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke zimmi ko maale-ghanimat sey hissa nahin milega agar-che wo musalmanon key sath dushman sey jang karen. 4- kuchh ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke jab zimmi musalmanon key sath jang mein shareek hon to in ko hissa diya jaeyga. 5- Zohri sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Yahud ki eik jamaat ko hissa diya jo aap key sath jang mein shareek thi."
1559,"Main Ash-ari qabila ki eik jamaat key sath Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas khaibar aaya , jin logon ney khaibar Fateh kiya tha aap ney unkey sath hamarey liye bhi hissey muqarrar kiye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Auzaai kehtey hain : ghodey key liye hissa muqarrar karney sey pehley jo musalmanon key sath mil jaey, us ko hissa diya jaeyga."
1560,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey majoos ki haandiyon key barey mein sawal kiya gaya padhi. to aap ney farmaya : ''un ko dho kar saaf kar lo aur un mein pakaao, aur aap ney har darindey aur kuchli waley janwer ko khaney sey mana farmaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Abu-Solba (Raziallahu anhu) sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai. 2- Abu-Idrees Khaulaani ney bhi is ko Abu-Solba sey riwayat kiya hai, lekin abu-Qulaba ka samaa (sun'na), Abu-Solba sey sabit nahin hai, unhoney abu-Asmaa key wastey sey Abu-Solba sey iski riwayat ki hai."
1561,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sariya key shuru mein janey par chothai hissey aur ladaai sey laut'tey waqt dobara janey par tihai hissey zayed bator inaam (nafl) detey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees abu-Salaam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, unhoney eik Sabab sey iski riwayat ki hai aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ki hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Habib bin Musallema, Ma'an bin Yazeed , ibne-Umar aur Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1562,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo kisi kafir ko qatl karey aur uskey paas gawah mojud ho to maqtool ka saman usi ka hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hadees main eik qissa mazkur (zikr hua) hai.
1563,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney taqseem sey pehley maale-ghanimat ki kharid aur farokht sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1564,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ( hamila ( qaidi aurton sey jima karney sey mana farmaya jab tak ke wo apney pet mein mojud bachchon ko jan na den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Arbaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ruwefie bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Auzaai kehtey hain ke jab koi shakhs qaidi aurton mein sey laundi khareedey aur wo hamila ho to is silsiley mein umr bin Khattab sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hamila jab tak bachcha na janey us sey sohbat nahin ki jaeygi. 4- Auzaai kehtey hain : azad aurton key silsiley main to ye sunnat chali aa rahi hai ke in ko iddat guzarney ka hukm diya gaya hai."
1565,Mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Nasara key khane key barey mein sawal kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''koi khana tumharey dil mein shak na paida karey ke uskey silsiley mein nasraniyat sey tumhari mushaabihat ho jaey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
1566,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''jisney maa aur uskey bachche key darmiyan judai paida ki, Allah qiyamat key din usey uskey doston sey juda kar dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai, wo log qaidiyon mein maa aur bachchey key darmiyan , baap aur bachchey key darmiyan aur bhaiyon key darmiyan judai ko napasand samajhtey hain."
1567,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Jibreel ney merey paas aa kar kaha : apney sathiyon ko Badr key qaidiyon key silsiley mein ikhtiyar den, wo chahen to unhen qatl karen, chahen to fidya lein, fidye ki surat mein un mein sey aainda saal itney hi aadmi qatl kiye jaeyngey, un logon ney kaha : fidya leingey aur hum mein sey qatl kiye jaeyn. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Sory ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, hum is ko sirf ibne-Abi zyada hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Abu-Usaama ney basanad (Hisham an ibne-Sirin an Ubaida an Ali an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai. 3- ibne Aun ney basanad (ibne-Sirin an Ubaida an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) mursalan riwayat ki hai. 4- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Anas , abu-Barza , aur Juber bin Mut-im sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1568,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Mushrekin key eik qaidi mard key badle mein do musalman mardon ko chhudwaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu-Qulaba ka naam Abdullah bin Zaid Jurmi hai. 3- aksar ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai ke Imam ko ikhtiyar hai ke qaidiyon mein sey jis par chahey ehsan karey aur jisey chahey qatl karey , aur jin sey chahey fidya ley. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney fidye key bajaey qatl ko ikhtiyar kiya hai. 5- Imam Auzaai kehtey hain ke mujhey ye khabar pahunchi hai ke ye aayat : (فإما منا بعد وإما فداء) mansookh hai, aur aayat : (واقتلوهم حيث ثقفتموهم) iskey liye naasikh hai. 6- Is-haq bin Mansoor kehtey hain ke mainey Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal sey sawal kiya : aap key nazdik kya behtar hai jab qaidi giraftar ho to usey qatl kiya jaey ya us sey fidya liya jaey, unhoney jawab diya, agar wo fidya ley saken to koi harj nahin hai aur agar unhen qatl kar diya jaey to bhi main is mein koi harj nahin samajhta. 7- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke merey nazdik khoon bahana ziyada behtar hai jab ye mashhoor ho aur aksar log uski khahish rakhtey hon."
1569,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kisi ghazwey main eik aurat maqtool pai gaee, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uski mazammat ki aur aurton aur bachchon key qatl sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Barida , Ribah , in ko Ribah bin Rabee bhi kehtey hain, Aswad bin Saee ibne-Abbas aur Sa'ab bin Jassama sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai, ye log aurton aur bachchon key qatl ko haram samajhtey hain, Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai ka bhi yehi qol hai. 3- kuch ehle-ilm ney raat mein un par chhapa maarney ki aur is mein aurton aur bachchon key qatl ki rukhsat di hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, in dono ney raat mein chhapa maarney ki rukhsat di hai."
1570,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey ghodon ney mushrekin ki aurton aur bachchon ko raund dala hai, aap ney farmaya : ''wo bhi apney baap-daada qisam sey hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1571,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein eik lashkar mein bheja aur farmaya : ''agar tum Quraish key falan falan do aadmiyon ko paao to unhen jala do.''  phir jab hamney rawangi ka irada kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''main ney tum ko hukm diya tha ke falan falan ko jala do halanke aag sey sirf Allah hi azab dega isliye ab agar tum in ko paao to qatl kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Muhammad bin Is-haq ney is hadees mein Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key darmiyan eik aur aadmi ka zikr kiya hai, kaee aur logon ney Les ki riwayat ki tarah riwayat ki hai, Les bin Saad ki hadees ziyada sahih hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1572,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo mar gaya aur teen chizon yani takabbur (ghamand), maale-ghanimat mein khayanat aur qarz sey bari raha , wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Abu-Hurera aur Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1573,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis key jism sey rooh nikli aur wo teen chizon yani khazana, ghulul aur qarz sey bari raha, wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.''  Saeed bin Abi Aruba ney isi tarah apni riwayat mein « الكنز » bayan kya hai aur abu awaana ney apni riwayat mein « الكبر » bayan kiya hai, aur is mein « an Maadaan » ka zikr nahin kiya hai, Saeed ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai."
1574,"arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! falan aadmi shaheed ho gaya, aap ney farmaya : ''hergiz nahin, mainey us abaa ( kapdey ( ki wajeh sey usey jahannam mein dekha hai jo usney maale ghanimat sey churaayaa tha.''  aap ney farmaya : ''Umar ! khadey ho jaao aur teen martaba aelan kar do , jannat mein momin hi dakhil hongey (aur momin aadmi khayanat nahin kiya kartey).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1575,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Umme Sulem aur unkey sath rehney wali ansaar ki chand aurton key sath jihad mein nikaltey they, wo pani pilaati aur zakhmiyon ka ilaj karti thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Rabee binte Muawwiz sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1576,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye Faras key badshah Kisraa ney aap key liye tohfa bheja to aap ney isey qubul kar liya, (kuchh) aur baadshaahon ney aap key liye tohfa bheja to aap ney unkey tohfey qubul kiye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Raavi Suwair Abu Faakhita key betey hain, Abu Faakhita ka naam Saeed bin Ilaaqa hai aur Suwair ki kunniyat abu-Jahm hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir sey bhi riwayat hai."
1577,"Unhoney ( Islam laney sey qabl ( Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko eik tohfa diya ya oontni hadiya ki, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : ''kya tum Islam la chukey ho?'' unhoney kaha : nahin, aap ney farmaya : ''mujhey to mushrikon key tohfo sey mana kiya gaya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qol :(إني نهيت an زبد المشركين) ka matlab ye hai ke mujhey in key tohfon sey mana kiya gaya hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap mushrikon key tohfey qubul farmatey they, jabke is hadees mein karaahat ka bayan hai, ehtimaal (gumaan) hai ke ye baad ka amal hai, aap pehley unkey tohfey qubul farmatey they, phir aap ney is sey mana farma diya."
1578,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik khabar aai , aap us sey khush huye aur Allah key samney sajde mein gir gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum is ko sirf isi sanad sey Bakkaar bin Abdul-Azeez ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- Bakkaar bin Abdul-Azeez bin Abi Bakra mqarib al hadees hain. 4- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo sajda shukar ko durust samajhtey hain."
1579,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''musalman aurat kisi ko panah dey sakti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey puchha to unhoney kaha : ye hadees sahih hai. 3- Kasir bin Zaid ney Waleed bin Ribah sey suna hai aur Waleed bin Ribah ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna hai aur wo maqarib al hadees hain. 4- is bab mein Umme-Haani (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1580,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur ehale Rome key darmiyan (kuchh muddat tak key liye) ehad aur paiman tha, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) unkey shehron mein jatey they taake jab ehad ki muddat tamam ho to un par hamla kar den, achcha eik aadmi ko apni sawari ya ghodey par : Allahu-akbar ! ''tumhari taraf sey wafaae ehad hona chahiye na ke bad-ehdi.'' , kehtey huye dekha wo Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) they, to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey iskey barey mein puchha , to unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jis aadmi key aur kisi qom key darmiyan ehad aur paiman ho to jab tak uski muddat khatam na ho jaey ya us ehad ko un tak barabari key sath wapis na kar dey, hergiz ehad na todey aur na naya ehad karey.''  Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko ley kar wapis lot aaye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1581,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''beshak ehad todne waley key liye qiyamat key din eik jhandaa nasab kiya (gaada) jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- mainey Muhammad sey Suwed ki is hadees key barey mein puchha jisey wo Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey , Abu-Is'haq ney Imaara bin Umer sey , Imaara ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''har ehad todney waley key liye eik jhandaa hoga.''  Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney kaha : merey ilm mein ye hadees marfoo nahin hai. 3- is bab mein Ali , Abdullah bin Masood , abu Saeed Khudri aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1582,"ghazwa ehzaab mein Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko teer laga , kuffar ney unki rage-ak'hal ya rage-abjal (bazu ki eik rag) kaat di, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney usey aag sey daagha to unka haath sooj gaya, lihaza aap ney usey chhod diya, phir khoon behney laga, chunanche aap ney dobara daagha phir unka haath sooj gaya, jab Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye dekha to unhoney dua ki : aey Allah! meri jaan us waqt tak na nikalna jab tak banu Qureza (ki halakat aur zillat sey) meri aankh thandi na ho jaey, pas unki rag ruk gaee aur khoon ka eik qatra bhi us sey na tapka, yahan tak ke banu-Qureza Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) key hukm par (qiley sey) nichey utrey, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Saad ko bulaya unhoney aa kar faisla kya ke unkey mardon ko qatl kar diya jaey aur aurton ko zinda rakha jaey, jin sey musalman khidmat lein, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum ney unkey barey mein Allah key faisla key muwaafiq faisla kya hai, unki tadaad chaar so thi, jab aap unkey qatl sey farigh huye to Saad ki rag khul gaee aur wo intiqal kar gaey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur Atiya Qurzi Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1583,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mushrekin key mardon ko qatl kar do aur unkey ladkon mein sey jo bulooghat ki umr ko na pahunchey hon unhen chhod do '' , « شرخ » wo ladkey hain jinkey zere-naaf key baal na nikley hon. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- Hujjaaj bin irtaat ney Qatada sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai."
1584,"hamen Qureza key din Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney pesh kya gaya, to jis key (zer-naaf key) baal nikley huye they usey qatl kar diya jata aur jis key nahin nikley hotey usey chhod diya jata, chunanche main un logon mein sey tha jin key baal nahin nikley they, lihaza mujhey chhod diya gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, agar bulooghat aur Umr malum na ho to wo log (zere-naaf key) baal nikalney hi ko bulooghat samajhtey they, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
1585,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney khutbey mein farmaya : '' jahiliyat key half (muahida taawun) ko pura karo, isliye ke ussey Islam ki mazbooti mein izafa hi hota hai aur ab Islam mein koi naya muahida taawun na karo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf, Umme-Salma, Juber bin Mut-im, Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas aur Qais bin Aasim (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1586,"main maqam manazir mein juz bin Muawiya ka munshi tha, hamarey paas umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka khat aaya ke tumhari taraf jo majoos hon unko dekho aur unsey jiziya lo kyonkey Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey khabar di hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maqame-hijr key majoosiyon sey jiziya liya tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1587,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) majoos sey jiziya nahin letey they yahan tak ke Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney unko khabar di ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maqam hijr key majoosiyon sey jiziya liya, is hadees mein us sey ziyada tafsil hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1588,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Behrein key majusiyon sey , aur umr aur Usman Raziallahu anhuma ney Faras key majusiyon sey jiziya liya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney bataya ke Malik riwayat kartey hain Zohri sey aur Zohri Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
1589,"mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! hum aisey logon key paas sey guzartey hain jo na hamari mehmani kartey hain, na un par jo hamara haq hai usey ada kartey hain, aur hum un sey kuch nahin letey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar wo na den siwaye uskey ke tum zabardasti un sey lo , to zabardasti ley lo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- isey Les bin Saad ney bhi Yazeed bin abi Habib sey riwayat kya hai (jaisa ke Bukhari ki sanad mein hai) 3- is hadees ka mafhoom ye hai ke Sahaba jihad key liye nikaltey they to wo eik aisi qom key paas sey guzartey, jahan khana nahin paatey they, ke qeemat sey khareedein, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar wo (khana) farokht karney sey inkar karen siwaye iskey ke tum zabardasti lo to zabardasti ley lo, 4- eik hadees mein isi tarah ki wazahat aai hai, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai, wo bhi isi tarah ka hukm diya kartey they."
1590,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fateh Makka key din farmaya : ''fatah-Makka key baad hijrat nahin hai lekin jihad aur niyat baqi hai, aur jab tum ko jihad key liye talab kya jaey to nikal pado ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sufiyan Sory ney bhi Mansoor bin Moatamir sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed , Abdullah bin Amr aur Abdullah bin Habshi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1591,"aayate-karima : (لقد رضي الله an المؤمنين إذ يبايعونك تحت الشجرة) ''Allah mominon sey razi ho gaya jab wo darkht key nichey aap sey baiat kar rahey they ''. ( Fateh : 18) key barey mein riwayat hai, Jabir kehtey hain ke hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey farar na honey ki baiat ki thi, hamney aap sey maut key ooper baiat nahin ki thi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees basanad (عيسى بن يونس an الأوزاعي an يحيى بن أبي كثير an جابر بن عبد الله) marvi hai, is mein Yahya bin abi Kasir aur Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma key darmiyan abu-Salma key wastey ka zikr nahin hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Salma bin Akwaa, ibne-Umar, Ubada aur Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1592,mainey Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Hudebia key din aap logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kis baat par baiat ki thi? unhoney kaha : maut par. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1593,"hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey samaa w taa-at (yani aap key hukm sunney aur aap ki itaat kerney) par baiat kartey they, phir aap hum sey farmatey : ''jitna tum sey ho sakey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - hadees Jabir aur hadees Salma bin Akwaa Raziallahu anhuma dono hadeeson ka maana sahih hai, (in mein taaruz nahin hai) baaz Sahaba ney aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey maut par baiat ki thi, un logon ney kaha tha : hum aap key samney ladtey rahengey yahan tak ke qatl kar diye jaeyn, aur doosrey logon ney aap sey baiat kartey huye kaha tha : hum nahin bhagengey۔"
1594,"hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey maut par baiat nahin ki thi, hamney to aap sey baiat ki thi ke nahin bhagengey (chahey uska anjam kabhi maut hi kyon na ho jaey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1595,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen aadmiyon sey qiyamat key din Allah Taala baat nahin kerega na hi unko gunahon sey pak kerega aur unkey liye dardnaak azab hai : eik wo aadmi jisney kisi Imam sey baiat ki phir agar Imam ney usey (uski marzi key mutabiq) diya to usney baiat puri ki aur agar nahin diya to baiat puri nahin ki''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur bila ikhtilaf usi key muwaafiq hukm hai.
1596,"eik ghulam aaya, usney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hijrat par baiat ki, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nahin jantey they ke wo ghulam hai, itney mein uska Malik aa gaya, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey usey bech do'', phir aap ney usko do kaley ghulam dekar kharid liya, uskey baad aap ney kisi sey baiat nahin li jab tak ussey ye na poochh letey ke kya wo ghulam hai? Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- hum is ko sirf abu-Zubair ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1597,"mainey kaee aurton key sath Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey baiat ki, aap ney hum sey farmaya : ''itaat is mein lazim hai jo tum sey ho sakey aur jiski tumhen taqat ho'', mainey kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool hum par khud hum sey ziyada meharban hain, mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! hum sey baiat liijiye (Sufiyan bin Uena kehtey hain : unka matlab tha musaafa keejiye), Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum so aurton key liye mera qol merey us qol jaisa hai jo eik aurat key liye hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, hum isey sirf Muhammad bin Munkadir hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Sufiyan Sory, Malik bin Anas aur kaee logon ney Muhammad bin Munkadir sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : main Umaima bint Raqiqa ki uskey ilawa dusri koi hadees nahin janta hun, 3- Umaima naam ki eik dusri aurat bhi hain jinki Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik hadees aai hai. 4- is bab mein Aaisha, Abdullah bin umr aur Asma bint Yazeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1598,"hum log kaha kartey they ke ghazwa Badr key din badri log tadaad mein Talut key sathiyon key barabar teen so terah they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sory aur doosrey logon ney bhi Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey uski riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1599,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney wafad abdul-Qais sey farmaya : ''main tum logon ko hukm deta hun ke maale-ghanimat sey khums (yani paanchwan hissey) ada karo, Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees main eik qissa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1600,"hum log eik safar mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they, jald baaz log aagey badhey aur ghanimat sey) khaney pakaaney ki cheezen) jaldi liya aur (taqseem sey pehley usey) pakaaney lagey, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam un sey peechey aaney waley logon key sath they, aap haandiyon key qarib sey guzrey to aap ney hukm diya aur wo ulat di gaeen, phir aap ney unkey darmiyan maale-ghanimat taqseem kya, aap ney eik oont ko das bakriyon key barabar qarar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sufiyan Sory ney ye hadees b-tareeq : (عن أبيه سعيد ، an عباية ، an جده رافع بن خديج) riwayat ki hai, is sanad mein abaaya ney apney baap key wastey ka nahin zikr kya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum sey is hadees ko Mehmood bin Ghelaan ney bayan kya wo kehtey hain : hum sey Wakee ney bayan kya, aur Wakee Sufiyan sey riwayat kartey hain. ye riwayat ziyada sahih hai, abaaya bin Rifaa ka samaa, unkey dada Raafey bin khadij sey Sabit hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Solba bin Hakam , Anas , abu-Rehana, Abu-Darda , Abdur-Rehman bin Samra, Zaid bin Khalid, Jabir, Abu-Hurera aur abu-Ayyub (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1601,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo loot-paat machaey wo hum mein sey nahin hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Anas ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
1602,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Yahud o Nasara ko salam karney mein pehal na karo aur un mein sey jab kisi sey tumhara aamna samna ho jaey to usey tang raastey ki janib janey par majbur kar do '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Anas (Raziallauh anhum) aur abu Basra ghifaari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - aur hadees ka mafhoom ye hai ke tum khud un sey salam na karo) balke unkey salam karney par sirf jawab do ( , 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : ye isliye napasand hai ke pehley salam karney sey un ki tazeem hogi jabke musalmanon ko unhen zaleel karney ka hukm diya gaya hai, isi tarah raastey mein aamna samna ho janey par unkey liye raasta na chhodey kyonkey is sey bhi unki tazeem hogi (jo sahih nahin hai) ."
1603,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''yahud mein sey koi jab tum logon ko salam karta hai to wo kehta hai : « السام عليک » ( yani tum par maut ho ( , isliye tum jawab mein sirf « عليک » kaho ( yani tum par maut ho ( ''."
1604,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qabila Khas-am ki taraf eik sariya rawana kya, ( kafiron key darmiyan rehney waley musalmanon mein sey) kuch logon ney sajdey key zariey panah chahi , phir bhi unhen qatl karney mein jaldi ki gaee , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko iski khabar mili to aap ney in ko aadhi diyat deney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : ''main har us musalman sey bariuzzimma hun jo mushrikon key darmiyan rehta hai'', logon ney puchha : Allah key Rasool! aakhir kyon? aap ney farmaya : '' (musalman ko kafiron sey itni doori par rehna chahiye ke) wo dono eik doosrey ( key khana pakaaney ( ki aag na dekh saken '' padhi. ."
1605,"abda ney ye hadees b-tareeq : « Ismael bin abi Khalid an Qais ibne-Abi an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ( mursalan ( abu-Muaawia key misl hadees riwayat ki hai, is mein unhon ( abda ( ney Jareer key wastey ka zikr nahin kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye riwayat ziyada sahih hai, 2- Ismail bin abi Khalid key aksar shagrid Ismail key wastey sey Qais bin abi Hazim sey) mursalan ( riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik sariya rawana kya, un logon ney is mein Jareer key wastey ka zikr nahin kya, aur Hammad bin Salma ney b-tareeq : (إسمعيل بن أبي خالد an قيس ابن أبي an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ( marfooan ( abu-Muaawia key misl uski riwayat ki hai, 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : sahih ye hai ke Qais ki hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursal hai, neez Samra bin Jundub ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, aap ney farmaya : '' mushrikon key sath na raho aur na unki hum nasheeni ikhtiyar karo, jo unkey sath rahega ya unki ham-nasheeni ikhtiyar kerega wo bhi unhi mein sey maana jaeyga, padhi. 2- is bab mein Samra sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1606,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar mein zinda raha to inshaAllah jazeera Arab sey Yahud o Nasara ko nikal bahar kar dunga''
1607,unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''main jazeera Arab sey Yahud o Nasara ko zarur nikaalunga aur is mein sirf musalman ko baqi rakhunga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1608,"Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aa kar kaha : aap ki wafat key baad aap ka waris kon hoga ? unhoney kaha : merey ghar waley aur meri aulad , Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : phir kya wajeh hai ke main apney baap ki waris na banun? abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai ke '' hum ( anbiya (ka koi waris nahin hota '' ( phir abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ( lekin Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jiski kafalat kartey they hum bhi uski kafalat kerengey aur aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jis par kharch kartey they hum bhi is par kharch kerengey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- isey Hammad bin Salma aur abdul-wahaab bin Ata ney musnadan riwayat kya hai ye dono aur Muhammad bin umr sey aur Muhammad abu-Salma sey , aur abu-Salma Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhon kaha : main Hammad bin Salma key ilawa kisi ko nahin janta hun jisney is hadees ko Muhammad bin Amr sey Muhammad ney abu-Salma sey aur abu-Salma ney Abu-Hurera sey) marfooan ( riwayat ki ho. ( Tirmizi kehtey hain : haan ( abdul-wahaab bin Ata ney bhi Muhammad bin Amr sey aur Muhammad ney abu-Salma sey aur abu-Salma ney Abu-Hurera sey Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat ki tarah riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Talha , Zuber , Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , Saad aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1609,"Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma key paas Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki meeras sey apna hissey talab karney ayen , un dono ney kaha : hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' mera koi waris nahin hoga '' , Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) bolin : Allah ki qism ! main tum dono sey kabhi baat nahin karun gi , chunanche wo intiqal kar gaeen , lekin un dono sey baat nahin ki. Raavi Ali bin Esa kehtey hain : « la أكلمكما » ka mafhoom ye hai ke main us meeras key silsiley mein kabhi bhi aap dono sey baat nahin karungi, aap dono sachey hain. (Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain ( ye hadees kaee sanadon sey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai."
1610,"mein umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya, usi doran unkey paas Usman bin Affaan , Zuber bin Awam , Abdur-Rehman bin Auf aur Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallauh anhum) bhi pahunchey , phir Ali aur Abbas Raziallahu anhuma jhagadtey huye aaye , umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : main tum logon ko us Allah ki qism deta hun jiskey hukm sey aasman o zamin qaaim hai, tum log jantey ho Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : '' hamara ( yani anbiya ka ( koi waris nahin hota , jo kuch hum chhodtey hain wo sadqa hota hai'' , logon ney kaha : haan ! umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam wafat paa gaey, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka janashin hun, phir tum apney bhatijey ki meeras mein sey apna hissa talab karney aur ye apni biwi key baap ki meeras talab karney key liye abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : beshak Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' hamara ( yani anbiya ka ( koi waris nahin hota , hum jo kuch chhodtey hain wo sadqa hota hai'' , ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ( Allah khub janta hai abu-Bakar sachey , nek , bhaley aur haq ki perwi karney waley they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees mein tafsil hai, ye hadees Malik bin Aus padhi. ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1611,"Fateh Makka key din mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' Makka mein aaj key baad qiyamat tak ( kafiron sey) jihad nahin kya jaeyga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. yani Zakariya bin abi zyada ki hadees jo Shaaby key wastey sey aai hai, 2- hum is hadees ko sirf un hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Sarad aur mutee (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1612,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath jihad kya, jab Fajr tulu hoti to aap ( qitaal sey) thehar jatey yahan tak ke suraj nikal jata, jab suraj nikal jata to aap jihad mein lag jatey , phir jab dophare hoti aap ruk jatey yahan tak ke suraj dhal jata, jab suraj dhal jata to aap Asr tak jihad kartey , phir thehar jatey yahan tak ke Asr padh letey , phir jihad ( shuru ( kartey . kaha jata tha ke us waqt nusrate-Ilaahi ki hawa chalti hai aur momin apney mujahidon key liye namaz mein duayen kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai jo mosul hai, Qatada ki mulaqat Noman sey nahin hai, Noman bin Muqrin ki wafat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key daure-khilaafat mein hui."
1613,"bin Khattab ney Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ko hurmuz unkey paas bheja , phir unhoney mukammal hadees bayan ki, Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath ( kisi ghazwey mein) hazir huwa , jab aap din key shuru hissey mein nahin ladtey to intizar kartey yahan tak ke suraj dhal jata, hawa chalney lagti aur nusrate-Ilaahi ka nuzool hota . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1614,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bad-faali shirk hai''. (ibne-Masood kehtey hain) hum mein sey koi aisa nahin hai jis key dil mein uska weham o khayal na paida ho, lekin Allah Taala us weham o khayal ko tawakkul ki wajeh sey zaayel kar deta hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, hum isey sirf Salma bin kuheil ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Shoba ney bhi Salma sey is hadees ki riwayat ki hai, Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Harab is hadees mein (وما منا ولكن الله يذهبه بالتوكل) ki baabat kehtey they ke (وما منا) merey nazdik Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol hai, 4- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Habis Tameemi, Aaisha, ibne-Umar aur Saad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayatein hain."
1615,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' eik ki bimari doosrey ko lag janey aur bad-faali o badshiguni ki koi haqiqat nahin hai padhi. aur mujh ko faal nek pasand hai'' , logon ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! faale-nek kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : ''achi baat''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1616,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye sunna achcha lagta tha ke jab kisi zarurat sey niklen to koi ya Rashid ya nNjeeh kahey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1617,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab kisi lashkar par ameer muqarrar kartey to usey khas apney nafs key barey mein Allah sey darney aur jo musalman unkey sath hotey unkey sath bhalai karney ki wasiyat kartey they, uskey baad aap farmatey : Allah key naam sey aur uskey raastey mein jihad karo, un logon sey jo Allah ka inkar karney waley hain, maale-ghanimat mein khayanat na karo, ehad na todo , musla na karo, bachon ko qatl na karo aur jab tum apney mushrik dushmanon key samney jaao to in ko teen mein sey kisi eik baat ki dawat do un mein sey jisey wo maan lein qubul kar lo aur unkey sath ladaai sey baaz raho : in ko Islam laney aur apney watan sey muhajrin key watan ki taraf hijrat karney ki dawat do, aur in ko bata do ke agar unhoney aisa kar liya to unkey liye wohi huquq hain jo muhajrin key liye hain aur unkey ooper wohi zimmedariyan hain jo muhajrin par hain, aur agar wo hijrat karney sey inkar karen to unko bata do ke wo badwi musalmanon ki tarah hongey, unkey ooper wohi ehkam jari hongey jo badwi musalmanon par jari hotey hain : maale-ghanimat aur Fai mein unka koi hissa nahin hai magar ye ke wo musalmanon key sath mil kar jihad keren, phir agar wo aisa karney sey inkar karen to un par Fateh yaab honey key liye Allah sey madad talab karo aur unsey jihad shuru kar do, jab tum kisi qiley ka muhaasra karo aur wo chahen ke tum in ko Allah aur uskey Nabi ki panah do to tum unko Allah aur uskey Nabi ki panah na do, balke tum apni aur apney sathiyon ki panah do, (uskey khilaf na karna) isliye ke agar tum apna aur apney sathiyon ka ehad todtey ho to ye ziyada behtar hai us sey ke tum Allah aur uskey Rasool ka ehad todo , aur jab tum kisi qiley ka muhaasra karo aur wo chahen ke tum in ko Allah key faisley par utaaro to unko Allah key faisley par mat utaaro balke apney faisley par utaaro, isliye ke tum nahin jantey ke unkey silsiley mein Allah key faisley par pahunch sakogey ya nahin'', aap ney isi tarah kuch aur bhi farmaya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Barida ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1618,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz Fajr key waqt hi hamla kartey they, agar aap Azan sun letey to ruk jatey warna hamla kar detey , eik din aap ney kaan lagaya to eik aadmi ko kehtey suna : (الله أكبر الله أكبر)‏‏‏‏ aap ney farmaya : ''fitrat ( Deen Islam ( par hai, jab us ney (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله) kaha, to aap ney farmaya : ''tu jahannam sey nikal gaya''. Hasan kehtey hain : hum sey abul-Waleed ney bayan kya, wo kehtey hain : hum sey Hammad bin Salma ney isi sanad sey usi key misl bayan kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
